/20180509001144/https://www.billboard.com/music/van-halen/chart-history/hot-mainstream-rock-tracks|archivedate=2018-05-09}}</ref>\n*[[John Mellencamp]] (46) <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/john-mellencamp/chart-history/hot-mainstream-rock-tracks|title=John Mellencamp Chart History|publisher=}}</ref>\n*[[Pearl Jam]] (45) <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/pearl-jam/chart-history/hot-mainstream-rock-tracks|title=Pearl Jam Chart History|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171020054402/http://www.billboard.com/music/pearl-jam/chart-history/hot-mainstream-rock-tracks|archivedate=2017-10-20}}</ref>\n*[[Aerosmith]] (44) <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/aerosmith/chart-history/hot-mainstream-rock-tracks|title=Aerosmith Chart History|publisher=}}</ref>\n*[[Rush (band)|Rush]] (42) <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/rush/chart-history/hot-mainstream-rock-tracks|title=Rush Chart History|publisher=}}</ref>\n*[[Metallica]] (36) (tie) <ref name=\"Metallica\">{{cite web|title=Metallica Chart History Mainstream Rock|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/metallica/chart-history/hot-mainstream-rock-tracks|website=billboard.com|publisher=Billboard Magazine|accessdate=21 March 2018|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171029045337/http://www.billboard.com/music/metallica/chart-history/hot-mainstream-rock-tracks|archivedate=29 October 2017}}</ref>\n*[[The Rolling Stones]] (36) (tie) <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/the-rolling-stones/chart-history/hot-mainstream-rock-tracks|title=The Rolling Stones Chart History|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171020050524/http://www.billboard.com/music/the-rolling-stones/chart-history/hot-mainstream-rock-tracks|archivedate=2017-10-20}}</ref>\n*[[R.E.M.]] (35) <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/rem/chart-history/hot-mainstream-rock-tracks|title=R.E.M. Chart History|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180509001144/https://www.billboard.com/music/rem/chart-history/hot-mainstream-rock-tracks|archivedate=2018-05-09}}</ref>\n\n===Songs with the most weeks on the Mainstream Rock chart===\n*\"[[So Cold (Breaking Benjamin song)|So Cold]]\" by [[Breaking Benjamin]] (62) <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/breaking-benjamin/chart-history/hot-mainstream-rock-tracks/song/450846|title=Breaking Benjamin So Cold Chart History|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180509001145/https://www.billboard.com/music/breaking-benjamin/chart-history/hot-mainstream-rock-tracks/song/450846|archivedate=2018-05-09}}</ref>\n*\"[[Cold (Crossfade song)|Cold]]\" by [[Crossfade (band)|Crossfade]] (56) (tie) <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/crossfade/chart-history/hot-mainstream-rock-tracks/song/440913|title=Crossfade Cold Chart History|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180509001144/https://www.billboard.com/music/crossfade/chart-history/hot-mainstream-rock-tracks/song/440913|archivedate=2018-05-09}}</ref>\n*\"[[Hemorrhage (In My Hands)]]\" by [[Fuel (band)|Fuel]] (56) (tie) <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/fuel/chart-history/hot-mainstream-rock-tracks/song/392876|title=Fuel Hemorrhage (In My Hands) Chart History|publisher=}}</ref>\n*\"[[Headstrong (Trapt song)|Headstrong]]\" by [[Trapt]] (55) <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/trapt/chart-history/hot-mainstream-rock-tracks/song/425101|title=Trapt Headstrong Chart History|publisher=}}</ref>\n*\"[[Loser (3 Doors Down song)|Loser]]\" by [[3 Doors Down]] (53) (tie) <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/3-doors-down/chart-history/hot-mainstream-rock-tracks/song/387038|title=3 Doors Down Loser Chart History|publisher=}}</ref>\n*\"[[Awake (Godsmack song)|Awake]]\" by [[Godsmack]] (53) (tie) <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/godsmack/chart-history/hot-mainstream-rock-tracks/